{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"0c6b42e06b","title":"在修改《破车不能再开评第四届第三次国民参政会》时加写的两段话","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"5c3e2cfe8f","index":0,"year":1947,"month":6,"day":4,"articleId":"0c6b42e06b"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji23","name":"毛泽东全集第23卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji23.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji23":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"a2948331d5","type":"paragraph","text":"在修改《破车不能再开","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji23","articleId":"0c6b42e06b"},{"id":"43d94e20c7","type":"paragraph","text":"评第四届第三次国民参政会》时加写的两段话","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji23","articleId":"0c6b42e06b"},{"id":"be07240c8a","type":"paragraph","text":"（1947年6月4日）另有一部分君主立宪派，他们不赞成将介石的君主专制，但希望蒋介石接受他们的君主立宪论，这次也参加了参政会。但是这个参政会连同蒋介石政府在一起，按照于斌主教在开幕词中所说，是辆破车。就在这次参政会开会的第一天，即五月二十日，南京六干爱国学生结队向参政会请愿，表示要饭吃，要和平，却被全城军警展开巷战，不许请愿。这个参政会的参政员们亦溜之大吉，不愿接受请愿。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji23","articleId":"0c6b42e06b"}],"page":{"id":"30b689ad13","publicationId":"maoquanji23","articleId":"0c6b42e06b","start":81,"end":81}}}},"__N_SSG":true}